GLOBAL VALIDITY RULES (CRITICAL)
------------------------------------------------------------

{% if not clustered %}
1. NO HALLUCINATION: only use assets provided in the input.
2. COVERAGE (mandatory): for EVERY asset, ensure BOTH:
    - Position constraints: at least one of {against_wall, corner, horizontal, vertical, left_of, right_of, in_front_of, behind_of, around}
    - Orientation constraints: at least one of {against_wall, corner, facing, align}
(against_wall/corner count as both position+orientation constraints)
3. Avoid contradictions:
    - Do not apply multiple directional constraints (left_of, right_of, in_front_of, behind_of) on the same (source, target) pair.
4. Constraints should be minimal and complementary, not redundant.
5. ALL numeric parameters MUST use Var references. Raw numeric literals are NOT allowed.
